title: Eat More Greens
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Pizza, Japanese, Western, Take-out, Bakery, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Est. in mid-2000s as a vegetarian cafe and bakery, then re-opened Mar 2016 with meat added to the menu. Find pizza bread, salads, sweets, baked goods, and other meals. Located a short walk from Tokyo Metro Nanboku Line Azabu Jyuban station, at 東京都港区麻布十番2-2-5.
